public class VertexSet extends com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.set.ObjectSet<Vertex>
A set of vertexes. Supports union(Set), intersection(Set) and without(Set) operations, that logically combine this set of vertexes with another set of vertexes without creating a physical one.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
